column5: Planning to open ice fishing this Saturday or Sunday but I'm a little bit concerned about ice.  Any information about these 2 lakes would be very appreciated.
Not sure anyone wants to give out ice conditions for concern of back lash if something were to happen to you.
I have not measured ice on six mile yet.  But it's was skimmed over in spots last time I drove by.  Likely 2' of snow on 3" of ice at best.
